title: District Council - Shapefile - Map
description:
This is the shapefile for St Paul's 17 District Councils.
Each of the Councils represent their neighborhood and their responsibilities include: planning and advising on the physical, economic, and social development of their areas; identifying needs; initiating community programs; recruiting volunteers; and sponsoring community events.

title: Council Ward - Shapefile - Map
description:
This shapefile presents the City of St Paul's 7 Wards.
Each ward is represented by a member on the City Council.

title: Saint Paul Police Grid - Shapefile
description: This shapefile represents the City of Saint Paul's Police Grids.
